        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "I must have your opinion too.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Hetty, run and tell your uncle to come in,\" said mrs Poyser, as they entered the house, and the old gentleman bowed low in answer to Hetty's curtsy; while Totty, conscious of a pinafore stained with gooseberry jam, stood hiding her face against the clock and peeping round furtively.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"And you keep it so exquisitely clean, mrs Poyser.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "I like these premises, do you know, beyond any on the estate.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Not yet; I must see your dairy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"I think I see the door open, there.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000020_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000020_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "I don't expect that mrs Satchell's cream and butter will bear comparison with yours.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"I can't say, sir, I'm sure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "It's seldom I see other folks's butter, though there's some on it as one's no need to see-the smell's enough.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Thank you, that really is a pleasant sight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Unfortunately, my slight tendency to rheumatism makes me afraid of damp: I'll sit down in your comfortable kitchen.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000022_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000022_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Ah, Poyser, how do you do?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "mr Poyser had just entered in shirt sleeves and open waistcoat, with a face a shade redder than usual, from the exertion of \"pitching.\" As he stood, red, rotund, and radiant, before the small, wiry, cool old gentleman, he looked like a prize apple by the side of a withered crab.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Will you please to take this chair, sir?\" he said, lifting his father's arm chair forward a little: \"you'll find it easy.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Do you know, mrs Poyser-sit down, pray, both of you-I've been far from contented, for some time, with mrs Satchell's dairy management.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "I think she has not a good method, as you have.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"And now, Poyser, as Satchell is laid up, I am intending to let the Chase Farm to a respectable tenant.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Now, the plan I'm thinking of is to effect a little exchange.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000032_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000032_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "On the other hand, Poyser, you might let Thurle have the Lower and Upper Ridges, which really, with our wet seasons, would be a good riddance for you. There is much less risk in dairy land than corn land.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "He was much too acute a man not to see through the whole business, and to foresee perfectly what would be his wife's view of the subject; but he disliked giving unpleasant answers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Say?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"That difficulty-about the fetching and carrying-you will not have, mrs Poyser,\" said the squire, who thought that this entrance into particulars indicated a distant inclination to compromise on mrs Poyser's part.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000041_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000041_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "But I don't want to part with an old tenant like you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142371_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142371/2817_142371_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Meanwhile the bull dog, the black and tan terrier, Alick's sheep dog, and the gander hissing at a safe distance from the pony's heels carried out the idea of mrs Poyser's solo in an impressive quartet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "The Eve of the Trial",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "AN upper room in a dull Stoniton street, with two beds in it-one laid on the floor.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "It is ten o'clock on Thursday night, and the dark wall opposite the window shuts out the moonlight that might have struggled with the light of the one dip candle by which Bartle Massey is pretending to read, while he is really looking over his spectacles at Adam Bede, seated near the dark window.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "His face has got thinner this last week: he has the sunken eyes, the neglected beard of a man just risen from a sick bed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "His heavy black hair hangs over his forehead, and there is no active impulse in him which inclines him to push it off, that he may be more awake to what is around him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "He is roused by a knock at the door.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Adam rose from his chair with instinctive respect, as mr Irwine approached him and took his hand.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"I'm late, Adam,\" he said, sitting down on the chair which Bartle placed for him, \"but I was later in setting off from Broxton than I intended to be, and I have been incessantly occupied since I arrived.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "I have done everything now, however-everything that can be done to night, at least. Let us all sit down.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Adam took his chair again mechanically, and Bartle, for whom there was no chair remaining, sat on the bed in the background.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Yes, Adam; I and the chaplain have both been with her this evening.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "As mr Irwine paused, Adam looked at him with eager, questioning eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Three or four days ago, before you were mentioned to her, when I asked her if there was any one of her family whom she would like to see-to whom she could open her mind-she said, with a violent shudder, 'Tell them not to come near me-I won't see any of them.'\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "She didn't seem agitated when I mentioned your name; she only said 'No,' in the same cold, obstinate way as usual. And if the meeting had no good effect on her, it would be pure, useless suffering to you-severe suffering, I fear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "She is very much changed...\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Adam started up from his chair and seized his hat, which lay on the table.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "But he stood still then, and looked at mr Irwine, as if he had a question to ask which it was yet difficult to utter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Bartle Massey rose quietly, turned the key in the door, and put it in his pocket.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Is he come back?\" said Adam at last.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"No, he is not,\" said mr Irwine, quietly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "I fear you have not been out again to day.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"You needn't be afraid of me. I only want justice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Arthur Donnithorne is not come back-was not come back when I left.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"But you don't mind about it,\" said Adam indignantly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Adam, he WILL know-he WILL suffer, long and bitterly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000021_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000021_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "No amount of torture that you could inflict on him could benefit her.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000024_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000024_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "But think of this: if you were to obey your passion-for it IS passion, and you deceive yourself in calling it justice-it might be with you precisely as it has been with Arthur; nay, worse; your passion might lead you yourself into a horrible crime.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000026_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000026_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Remember what you told me about your feelings after you had given that blow to Arthur in the Grove.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "Adam was silent: the last words had called up a vivid image of the past, and mr Irwine left him to his thoughts, while he spoke to Bartle Massey about old mr Donnithorne's funeral and other matters of an indifferent kind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"He is come; he is in Stoniton to night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "His own mind is in a very perturbed state, and it is best he should not see you till you are calmer.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"no",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "\"Yes, I did.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "I had a conversation with her-she pleased me a good deal. And now you mention it, I wish she would come, for it is possible that a gentle mild woman like her might move Hetty to open her heart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2817_142380_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2817/142380/2817_142380_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2817",
        "content": "God bless you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]